WEBVTT

00:07.314 --> 00:09.306
<i>Previously
on</i> Penny Dreadful...

00:10.697 --> 00:12.820
<i>You chase this son
of a bitch from London</i>

00:12.845 --> 00:14.776
to here in the middle
of the Devil's asshole

00:14.777 --> 00:16.017
because it's your duty?

00:16.149 --> 00:17.899
<i>I think there's more to Mr. Talbot</i>

00:17.924 --> 00:19.046
<i>than meets the eye.</i>

00:20.388 --> 00:21.438
<i>There's the tragedy of it.</i>

00:21.463 --> 00:23.284
The serum only lasts
a matter of hours...

00:23.285 --> 00:24.375
<i>and then they revert.</i>

00:24.376 --> 00:26.477
I believe I can increase the
duration of the change,

00:26.478 --> 00:27.806
perhaps even render it permanent.

00:27.853 --> 00:29.813
We'll create a choir of angels.

00:29.838 --> 00:31.680
<i>One in particular.</i>

00:31.728 --> 00:33.735
If we cannot save our son,

00:33.760 --> 00:35.791
the darkness will overcome the Earth.

00:35.792 --> 00:37.954
And all our days will come to an end.

00:40.017 --> 00:41.147
<i>Once we go into the desert,</i>

00:41.148 --> 00:41.931
we don't stop.

00:41.970 --> 00:43.931
- And then?
- My father.

00:43.932 --> 00:45.032
A homecoming, is it?

00:45.385 --> 00:46.475
Why are you here?

00:46.476 --> 00:48.497
I want to liberate your truest self...

00:48.498 --> 00:50.939
The beast that prowls around your heart.

00:51.163 --> 00:54.106
I want to rule the
darkness at your side.

